Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.18,0:01:09.02,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}湧上心頭的 感動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.94,0:01:19.11,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}沐浴著湛藍的陽光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:23.47,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}你迎風前行的身姿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.79,0:01:30.15,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}讓我陶醉時 目光相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.27,0:01:35.01,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我們齊聲歡笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.86,0:01:42.28,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}就像那 小小漩渦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.15,0:01:49.06,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,1000)\an3}無論何時 都想揮動雙手的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.94,0:01:53.35,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}確實是 曾經
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.74,0:01:58.88,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}與你同在的印記
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.63,0:02:03.23,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}永遠如 小小漩渦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.64,0:02:13.02,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我們的前方 道路在延伸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.44,0:02:21.75,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}攀上 下一個陡坡後
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.54,0:02:26.51,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,1000)}我們再相見吧
